OL,3,CDangerous cyclists could face tougher
OL,4,Cprison sentences under new proposals
OL,6,FCyclists who kill or injure
OL,7,Fpedestrians could face tougher
OL,8,Fpunishments under new government
OL,9,Fplans, as ITV News Reporter Natasha
OL,10,FPotts explains
OL,12,FDangerous cyclists could face tougher
OL,13,Fsentences similar those enforced on ,
OL,14,Funder new proposals being debated in
OL,15,FParliament on Wednesday.
OL,17,FThe move would close a loophole which
OL,18,Fhas been campaigned against for years,
OL,19,Fthat only allows a to be jailed for a
OL,20,Fmaximum of two years for "wanton and
OL,21,Ffurious driving".
