OL,3,CDangerous cyclists could face tougher
OL,4,Cprison sentences under new proposals
OL,6,FFormer leader of the Party Sir Iain
OL,7,FDuncan Smith has put forward a number
OL,8,Fof amendments to the Criminal Justice
OL,9,FBill being debated on Wednesday
OL,10,Fafternoon, which would mean people
OL,11,Friding bikes would face tougher
OL,12,Fpenalties if they injure of kill
OL,13,Fpedestrians.
