OL,3,CDangerous cyclists could face tougher
OL,4,Cprison sentences under new proposals
OL,6,FThe amendments would cover people
OL,7,Friding pedal bikes, e-bikes, electric
OL,8,Fscooters, unicycles and "personal
OL,9,Ftransporters".
OL,11,FPosting on X, Sir Iain said:
OL,12,F"Ministers have repeatedly promised to
OL,13,Fupdate laws but have repeatedly failed
OL,14,Fto do so."
